Oru Indian Pranayakatha (2013)


-:Release Info:-

Oru Indian Pranayakatha is a 2013 Malayalam romantic comedy film written by Ikbal Kuttipuram and directed by Sathyan Anthikad. The film stars Fahadh Faasil and Amala Paul in the lead roles.
